scriptlet.name: default
default

staticBinding.value:
SELECT RESPOOLID, MAXDISK,HPIO, VMMP_IP FROM ( SELECT UNIQUE(M.RESPOOLID),M.MAXDISK,CC.HPIO,VMMP.IP AS VMMP_IP, M.MAXSYS - M.ALLOCSYS AS FREESYS FROM RVW_MOERESPOOLALLOC M INNER JOIN CLOUDCELL CC ON M.CCNAME = CC.CCNAME INNER JOIN DATACENTER DC ON CC.DCNAME = DC.DCNAME LEFT JOIN RESPOOL_VMMP RES_VM ON M.RESPOOLID = RES_VM.RESPOOLID LEFT JOIN VMMP VMMP ON CC.CCNAME = VMMP.CCNAME AND RES_VM.VMMP_TYPE = VMMP.VMMP_TYPE WHERE CC.CATNAME = '${db.getresourcepool.catname}' ${db.getresourcepool.ccname.query} ${db.getresourcepool.dcacronym.query} AND M.SLALEVEL = '${db.getresourcepool.slalevel}' AND M.SYSTEMTYPE = '${db.getresourcepool.systemtype}' AND M.MAXSYS - M.ALLOCSYS > 0 AND VMMP.VMMP_TYPE ='${db.getresourcepool.vmmp.type}'
UNION
SELECT UNIQUE(M.RESPOOLID),M.MAXDISK,CC.HPIO, NULL AS VMMP_IP, M.MAXSYS - M.ALLOCSYS AS FREESYS FROM RVW_MOERESPOOLALLOC M INNER JOIN CLOUDCELL CC ON M.CCNAME = CC.CCNAME INNER JOIN DATACENTER DC ON CC.DCNAME = DC.DCNAME INNER JOIN TSHIRTSIZES SZ ON M.SYSTEMTYPE = (SZ.HARDWARE || SZ.TSIZE) WHERE CC.CATNAME = '${db.getresourcepool.catname}' ${db.getresourcepool.ccname.query} ${db.getresourcepool.dcacronym.query} AND M.SLALEVEL = '${db.getresourcepool.slalevel}' AND M.SYSTEMTYPE = '${db.getresourcepool.systemtype}' AND M.MAXSYS - M.ALLOCSYS > 0 )
ORDER BY FREESYS DESC

SELECT V.VMTPLLOC,V.VMTPLGUID, V.VMTPLNAME FROM VMTEMPLATES V WHERE V.RESPOOLID = '${db.getresourcepool.resourcepool}' AND V.OS = '${db.getresourcepool.os}' AND V.ISCLIENTSUPPLIED='${server.1.isclientsupplied}' AND V.VMTPLNAME='${server.1.templatename}'

SELECT a.VMTPLNAME FROM VMTEMPLATES a, MOERESPOOL b WHERE a.RESPOOLID=b.RESPOOLID AND a.OS='${db.getresourcepool.os}' AND a.ISCLIENTSUPPLIED='${server.1.isclientsupplied}' AND b.CCNAME='${db.getresourcepool.ccname}' AND b.SLALEVEL='SLA1' AND b.SYSTEMTYPE='V' AND a.VMTPLNAME = '${server.1.templatename}'
SELECT V.VMTPLLOC,V.VMTPLGUID, V.VMTPLNAME FROM VMTEMPLATES V WHERE V.RESPOOLID = '${db.getresourcepool.resourcepool}' AND V.OS = '${db.getresourcepool.os}' AND ISCLIENTSUPPLIED is NULL
